{"tid":2342890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］即使經歷再黑暗嘅時刻，當年嘅勇武亦無放棄過香港重光嘅希望","createTime":"2020-12-27T13:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T08:13:33.000Z","uid":188515,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a53ad1ac4d83c33c259bae5d0c5d467650630642","tid":2342890,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"好多人都以為一場戰爭嘅終結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就代表反抗徹底咁失敗，而去放棄<br />\n但其實一場真正嘅反抗運動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n並<span class=\"gold\">唔會以一場戰爭嘅失敗畫上句號</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEScqFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEScqFL.jpg&h=57911e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺三年零八個月嘅日治時期<br />\n香港嘅戰俘<span class=\"gold\">都無放棄重光嘅希望</span><br />\n默默咁堅持到最後嘅勝利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NeFNeza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNeFNeza.jpg&h=d9227947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲們有睇過我上個Post嘅<br />\n應該記得喺1941年嘅香港保衛戰中<br />\n日軍喺佔有絕對優勢嘅情況下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n守軍都係寡不敵眾宣佈投降<br />\n開啟往後<span class=\"gold\">三年零八個月嘅日治時期</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCkYmef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCkYmef.jpg&h=13fbe9d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而其實喺香港淪陷期間<br />\n就一共有10, 947人成為日軍戰俘<br />\n被日軍囚禁喺深水埗、亞皆老街<br />\n馬頭涌同北角嘅戰俘營 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來部份人被送到日本同台灣充當苦力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cxoxkZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cxoxkZ.jpg&h=abb7ada5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時亦有2000名盟國市民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被送到前身聖士提反書院嘅赤柱拘留營<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WnUimeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWnUimeo.jpg&h=570a7ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而由於日軍缺乏準備<br />\n戰俘好快面臨糧食同醫療用品嘅短缺<br />\n加上戰俘經常被日軍奴役 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令本身營養不良嘅戰俘<br />\n受盡疾病與奴役嘅折磨而死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WkH7Y09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWkH7Y09.jpg&h=38ce0aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而根據軍事歷史學家嘅統計<br />\n喺1942-1944年間<br />\n就有過千戰俘喺海上同各地戰俘營死去<br />\n單係運載戰俘嘅貨船里斯本丸被擊沉<br />\n就造成接近800人死亡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQW1i1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQW1i1e.jpg&h=396728b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而對於營內戰俘遭受嘅苦況<br />\n英國當局為咗激發軍隊抗擊敵人<br />\n於是公開咗戰俘的待遇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加軍嘅徵兵海報亦以<span class=\"gold\">記着香港</span>為口號<br />\n呼籲市民參軍對抗日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i4BsY1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi4BsY1n.jpg&h=b247950f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而隨着戰局嘅發展，唔少戰俘開始逃走<br />\n其中防衛軍醫官賴廉士上校<br />\n就喺1942年1月成功逃脫<br />\n成立咗<span class=\"gold\">英軍服務團</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺華南地區營救戰俘同收集情報<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcN7Y1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxcN7Y1s.jpg&h=b9267a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺1942年秋開始<br />\n戰俘就按照英軍服務團嘅指引<br />\n策劃一場大規模嘅逃脫行動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其中國共兩黨嘅游擊隊、美軍<br />\n同埋前華籍軍人、警員都會一齊行動<br />\n亦即<span class=\"gold\">代號「筷子行動」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2tGi1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2tGi1y.jpg&h=13e97e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但後來，日軍成功破獲呢次嘅計劃<br />\n並喺全港大肆搜捕可疑人物<br />\n對佢地施以嚴刑逼供<br />\n處決咗大批主要參與者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzadUz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzadUz5.jpg&h=4a55cd8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，隨著盟軍開始全面反攻<br />\n戰俘嘅身體亦因為海運中斷而變差<br />\n而身在香港與日本各地嘅戰俘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更要面對盟軍日以繼夜空襲同砲轟<br />\n戰爭結束時，就有2,184名戰俘死亡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWXPsU9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWXPsU9.jpg&h=ae57ef14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然戰俘過着非常艱苦嘅生活<br />\n但佢地都無放棄過重光嘅希望<br />\n一直<span class=\"gold\">保持樂觀嘅心態過活</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyPx98A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyPx98A.jpg&h=1e129100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而隨著美軍喺8月<br />\n向日本扔咗兩粒原子彈<br />\n而蘇聯亦向日本宣戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進攻日本佔據嘅滿州國同華北地區<br />\n日本亦向盟軍<span class=\"gold\">宣佈無條件投降 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/toTyUAj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtoTyUAj.jpg&h=e2136cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終，喺8月30日<br />\n夏慤將軍率領英國艦隊抵達香港<br />\n解放各個戰俘營同拘留營 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而幾千名倖存嘅香港戰俘<br />\n亦<span class=\"gold\">終於迎嚟重光嘅一日 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZ8SqG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZ8SqG2.jpg&h=caa5354a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年<span class=\"gold\">為香港犧牲嘅義士</span> <br />\n英軍服務團「M組」首領雷福榮 <br />\n（???-1943）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXJbGft.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXJbGft.png&h=dcc29f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參謀長紐臨上校<br />\n（1889-1943） <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JvEqLHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJvEqLHb.jpg&h=384f96cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n皇家蘇格蘭營的霍德上尉<br />\n（1918-1943） <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXv9sVD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXv9sVD.png&h=91fe77e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拉吉普營的印軍上尉安沙里<br />\n（1916-1943）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnZeD2n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnZeD2n.jpg&h=394bc50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印軍上尉安沙里嘅臨終遺言：<br />\n「人終需一死，很多人因病離世，承受揮之不去的痛楚。我們會堅強而健康地死去，<span class=\"gold\">全為信念，不作叛徒，高貴地為國捐軀。</span>我們如今避不過敵人的劍了，但無人應流淚或抱憾，我們要含笑面對敵人，勇敢地命赴黃泉。」<br />\n<br />\n毋忘老兵嘅付出<br />\n1941.12.7-1945.8.15<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料內容嚟自Movistory條片<br />\n有興趣知多啲嘅就睇條片<br />\n支持下<span class=\"gold\">黃色文創圈</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOhBIWchf08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQOhBIWchf08&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=65c7678c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOhBIWchf08</a>"},{"pid":"ca8b459c55d52e37130e7355af9ab94787238b1c","tid":2342890,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:04:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c788ce0dc31bf281aa618ab83ce4a8e639a353","tid":2342890,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09df4bf743d5a79ff088186c3f962c6874cd11e","tid":2342890,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7179b53d7fb0f27e33a2809196ea6d0412a13e0d","tid":2342890,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d9ac7286050c2bb1bf50286f89a187bef02854","tid":2342890,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n正評+CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09ad05e84d90a568529c173fbff04f1967ee322","tid":2342890,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高汁"},{"pid":"7d6d9a7b0307e2465d20ee312b66dcc8f9b0eeab","tid":2342890,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:15:08.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"db7f6e72bcce0877b54ebe078a5713d5482af894","tid":2342890,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fccf6e8a59a3583147d7f0882073c61b79417f5","tid":2342890,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\"